    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570760/extras/6ad5562fcf8e7bd2bfbb7c99eeaa35eb.avif?t=1702878040\" width=230 height=86 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >联系我们</h2>QQ群：812440943<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570760/extras/a6677d6916c9fff6d32ff99dac406241.avif?t=1702878040\" width=616 height=280 /></span><br>两年前，我们将塔防游戏和roguelike游戏相结合，制作出了变量这款单机塔防游戏<br><br>沉淀了两年时间后，我们经过思考重新制作了变量的这款续作！<br>变量2是一款独特的单机塔防游戏，我们丰富了塔防内的搭建和要素，并使游戏内的体验可以根据你的想法来进行变化！快一起来看看吧！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570760/extras/85d16a411af5a55d0fe6821c6c074ebf.avif?t=1702878040\" width=616 height=192 /></span><li>自由的路线搭建。不同于传统塔防，在《变量2》中你可以自由放置核心和出怪口的位置，然后通过利用路面、建筑物和地图中原有的物件去铺设一条有利于你的道路。与前作不同的是，这次你要面临的地形将会更加复杂。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570760/extras/a9c3d3f4c7f614fdf6022c1c0eddf0e5.avif?t=1702878040\" width=609 height=380 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570760/extras/a05fd839829ff5882cbf8e027c9e51a2.avif?t=1702878040\" width=616 height=192 /></span><br></li><li>防御塔的配方与合成。在《变量2》中，我们为你提供了5种基础塔和众多的高级塔。获得补给，抽取基础塔，然后根据配方去合成更强力的高级塔。高级塔拥有更高的属性和更强力的特性，合理的利用防御塔的搭配去面对各种不同的局面。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570760/extras/798d71c8176998700f70bd9b96027458.avif?t=1702878040\" width=616 height=192 /></span><br></li><li>装备。你可以为防御塔搭配装备。装备不仅仅是提供基础属性，更重要的是装备拥有许多特别的机制，合理的利用这些机制你的输出将会有爆炸的提升。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570760/extras/944264a2d4c2d1ed3f95d80e51f5a584.avif?t=1702878040\" width=218 height=300 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570760/extras/d403ed19825daf2306f2a0413da38816.avif?t=1702878040\" width=220 height=300 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570760/extras/ae81ee82328cd2bc22e581e6c15f1098.avif?t=1702878040\" width=616 height=192 /></span><br></li><li>插件。插件将为你提供一些额外的帮助，但你想要获得这些帮助则需要接受一些小小的挑战。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570760/extras/451d5eb6823b9f2d43e5103309a1404d.avif?t=1702878040\" width=290 height=396 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570760/extras/9665d386363bbd7178b45837cf4dcc42.avif?t=1702878040\" width=290 height=394 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1570760/extras/88ece81f161cf4f066846f94e23c7f25.avif?t=1702878040\" width=616 height=192 /></span><br></li><li>碎片组。装备和插件的获取将不同于前作的随机获得，而是你可以在游戏进入前使用碎片组去提前安排你的装备和插件的获取。碎片组的获得则是用游戏内获取的金钱进行抽取。</li></ul>",
